Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: US troops in Lebanon
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043x9zz
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 18 Sep 1983
Congress queries continued presence of US troops in Lebanon. President requested to invoke War Powers Act. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less